title: Chance The Rapper & DJ Khaled Hit The Studio
text:
Home > Music > Chance The Rapper & DJ Khaled Hit The Studio Chance The Rapper & DJ Khaled Hit The Studio 0 0 Posted by Danny Schwartz , Jan 16, 2017 at 12:51am Chance and Khaled are up to something. Chance the Rapper is the toast of the town these days. Everyone wants a piece of him, even Snapchat Jesus, DJ Khaled . Khaled scored some precious Chance face-to-face time this weekend in the studio. On Instagram, he shared a couple images of the two of them in what appears to be serious discussion: "FAN LUV Im in the studio wit @chancetherapper IM UP TO SOMETHING " Khaled wrote. "🔑 🦁🔑 @wethebestmusic ! BLESS UP!! FAN LUV EVERYTING TOP SECRET!!!!🙏🔑🙏🦁🔑" Chance and Khaled last linked up for the "No Problem" music video. Also of note: Khaled also played some street hockey with J-Biebs today. All in all, it's been a productive weekend.
